":guilabel:`Client ID` en :guilabel:`Client Secret` en :guilabel:`Save` de "
"instellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth.rst:129
msgid ""
"To configure the external Gmail account, return to the top of the "
